  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为教育数据整合项目设计一个流程图，核心是解决不同系统间词汇标准不一致的问题。起点应该是学生数据库，这是所有数据的源头。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UserStories",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以StudentDB是整个流程的入口。接下来需要判断什么？是判断词汇是否已经存在吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VocabExists",
        "Education_StudentDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，要加一个判断节点，检查教育领域是否已经存在可用的标准词汇库。这个判断会影响后面的走向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VocabExists"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我添加了VocabExists判断节点。如果答案是否定的，我们需要引入领域专家参与对吧？我注意到LMS门户是专家交互的主要界面。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EngageDomainExperts",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错。但还有另一条分支——如果词汇已存在，我们要判断它是否符合FAIR原则。这里需要GradeSync系统来做质量评估。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IsVocabFAIR",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加IsVocabFAIR判断节点。那么如果评估通过，直接采用现有词汇？如果没通过呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IsVocabFAIR",
        "AdoptFAIRVocabulary"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "通过的话直接采用，接入LMS门户。没通过的话，需要ContentCDN来重新构建或优化词汇，让它符合FAIR标准。这个节点比较特殊，是执行性的动作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MakeVocabularyFAIR",
        "Education_ContentCDN",
        "AdoptFAIRVocabulary"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "理解了。那从EngageDomainExperts这条线过来，也是指向MakeVocabularyFAIR吗？专家参与后共同制定标准词汇？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EngageDomainExperts",
        "MakeVocabularyFAIR"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，两条路径最终都汇聚到MakeVocabularyFAIR。优化完成后，再统一接入AdoptFAIRVocabulary节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MakeVocabularyFAIR",
        "AdoptFAIRVocabulary"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "流程结构完成了。我注意到MakeVocabularyFAIR应该做成虚线边框，表示这是一个可点击的参考节点，链接到FAIR词汇指南网站。",
